                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Lisbon</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-08-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 24, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Manuel Arriaga was to-day elected on first ballot President of Portugal by 121
                    votes of the Constituent Assembly. His principal opponent, Bernardino Machado,
                    received 86 votes.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Morgan.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
